snippet.title: Amiga Lotus Turbo Challenge 2 Intro OST High Quality
snippet.description:
Composed by Barry Leitch

Recorded straight from game with Audacity on ASUS Xonar DGX sound card using WinUAE to emulate Amiga Paula OCS (MOS8364, 4 channels 8-bit PCM chip) sound.
